INSTALLATION:

    0) Expand lv archive, using gunzip/tar.
    1) Change your working directory to ``(extracted sub directory)/build''.
    2) Execute ``../src/configure'' to configure compiler flags.
    3) Launch ``make''.
    4) Then, launch ``make install'' as root.

